    <p><img src="http://img01.inmotionhosting.com/_img/cpanel-hosting/security.jpg" />Security</p>
    <p><b>Secure your server through with cPanel tools.</b> cPanel gives you the option to protect your server by keeping unwanted access out. With cPanel, you can  block a single, or an entire range of IP addresses, manage SSL/TLS keys, connect to your server remotely through SSH, and more!</p>

    <p><img src="http://img01.inmotionhosting.com/_img/cpanel-hosting/email-administration.jpg" />Email Administration</p>
    <p><b>Keep your business communications professional.</b> Create email accounts with your domain as the address. With cPanel you can create multiple email addresses, setup email forwarding, access webmail, and get information on how to setup email on popular programs such as Outlook and Thunderbird.</p>
</div>

